1. What is "conditional rendering"?
whether or not something to get displayed or When we want to only sometimes
display something on the page

2. What would you use &&?
when you want to either display something or NOT display It

3. When would you use a ternary?
When you need to decide which thing amount 2 options to display

4. What if you need decide between > 2 options on What to display?
use an `if ... else if ... else` conditional or a `switch` statement
